Class LinkedDateTimeTripletMap.LinkedTriplet

java.lang.Object
org.krmdemo.techlabs.core.datetime.DateTimeTriplet
org.krmdemo.techlabs.core.datetime.LinkedDateTimeTripletMap.LinkedTriplet
Enclosing class:
LinkedDateTimeTripletMap<Key>
public static class LinkedDateTimeTripletMap.LinkedTriplet extends DateTimeTriplet
Extension to DateTimeTriplet that allows to link that triplet with sequentially previous and next triplets in corresponding collection or map.

    • getLinkedYearAndMonth

      public String getLinkedYearAndMonth()
      Returns:
      the value of DateTimeTriplet.getYearAndMonth() followed by dash'-'-symbol, if it's not the same as in previous item in sequence (otherwise - empty string)

    • getLinkedDayOfMonthAndWeek

      public String getLinkedDayOfMonthAndWeek()
      Returns:
      the value of DateTimeTriplet.getDayOfMonthAndWeek(), if getLinkedYearAndMonth() is not empty and if DateTimeTriplet.getDayOfMonthAndWeek() is not the same as of the previous item in sequence (otherwise - empty string)

    • getLinkedHoursMinutes

      public String getLinkedHoursMinutes()
      Returns:
      the value of DateTimeTriplet.getDayOfMonthAndWeek(), if getLinkedYearAndMonth() is not empty and if DateTimeTriplet.getHoursMinutes() is not the same as of the previous item in sequence (otherwise - dash'-'-symbol instead of digits)

    • dumpLinked

      public String dumpLinked()
      Returns:
      the same as inherited DateTimeTriplet.dump(), but skip displaying the values of parts, if they repeat the same of the previous item in sequence

    • dumpLinkedReversed

      public String dumpLinkedReversed()
      Returns:
      the same as inherited DateTimeTriplet.dump(), but skip displaying the values of parts, if they repeat the same of the next item in sequence
